{"tid":932488,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"人民力量擬年底發動「城市游擊戰」爭取普選","createTime":"2018-12-07T18:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T23:08:27.000Z","uid":224625,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1bddf751adf71f7dfe0f1ab434d7ebe8b0c9485a","tid":932488,"uid":224625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T18:41:18.000Z","msg":"人民力量陳偉業說，計劃年底發動「城市游擊戰」爭取真普選，但規模會比「佔領中環」行動小，希望約有2千人參與，讓中央看到港人對真普選的訴求，並表明香港人才是香港的主場。<br />\n<br />\n他舉例，若有10輛車同一時間在中環壞車，已能令中環半癱瘓，強調發動抗爭是要中央害怕，正視港人訴求。至於會否擔心行動違法，陳偉業說，站出來便不會怕，他正準備「不合作運動」小冊子，日後向市民派發，介紹行動。<br />\n<br />\n另外，陳偉業說，真普聯提出的3個政改建議，未能達到普及而民主的原則，人民力量今晚會開會，討論是否接受方案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F%E6%93%AC%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E7%99%BC%E5%8B%95-%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%B8%B8%E6%93%8A%E6%88%B0-%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%E6%99%AE%E9%81%B8-022900514.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%2587%258F%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%2595%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%258B%2595-%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%2588%25B0-%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%2599%25AE%25E9%2581%25B8-022900514.html&d=JrjjEcaI1qRAJKZ60pohMWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=0acf6807\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F%E6%93%AC%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E7%99%BC%E5%8B%95-%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%B8%B8%E6%93%8A%E6%88%B0-%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%E6%99%AE%E9%81%B8-022900514.html</a><br />\n<br />\n又到年底，今年有未???"},{"pid":"a409ee7067c0a5783b21b7b74abe349cf9a8744c","tid":932488,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T23:08:27.000Z","msg":"返鄉下打飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}